<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>로그인</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a7661af9ea.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a7661af9ea.css" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <style type="text/css">
        body{
            padding-top: 80px;
        }

    </style>

</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-sm-offset">
            <h1><i class="fas fa-sign-in"></i>회원가입</h1>
            <%if(message.length>0){%>
            <div class="alert alert-danger"><%=message%></div>
            <%}%>

            <form action="/signup" method="post">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>이메일</label>
                    <input type="email" class="form-control" name="email"/>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>비밀번호</label>
                    <input type="password" class="form-control" name="pwd"/>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>이름</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="name"/>
                </div>
                <br/>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning btn-lg">회원가입</button>
            </form>
            <hr/>
            <p>이미 계정이 있으세요? <a href="/login">로그인</a>
                <a href="/profile">회원정보</a>
            </p>
            <p><a href="/">홈으로</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    
</body>
</html>